$a(\tau )$ and $\phi(\tau)$ (dashed) in the Einstein frame for $k=1$,
  $m=\frac{1}{2}$, $\LL =3.1$}   \hfill
\end{minipage}
\hfill
\begin{minipage}[t]{7.3cm} \hfill
 \mbox{\epsfig{file=bild4.ps,height=10cm,width=7cm}} \vspace{-27mm} \par
